description:
The long awaited and highly acclaimed series is back! CABO the return, Part 4.
At the end of Cabo part 3, Sgt. Major takes Jenya for training miles away from the villa and into hot Mexican heat., Jenya is in for the training of her life. The Sgt. Runs her though an obstacle course military style and ties her up hogtied style. In the end she is begging to return to the villa with a new and improved attitude
If you missed Cabo 1-3 scroll down and watch them; it sets up the entire fantasy we have laid before you.
title: Cabo, the Return. Part 4
